Package es.ucm.fdi.tp.practica6.responses

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Response
    Represents a Response that the server gives to the clients connected.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangeTurnResponse
    Represents the response given by a server when there is a change of turn.
    ChatMessageResponse
    Represents a chat message response.
    ErrorResponse
    Represents an error response.
    GameOverResponse
    Represents a response that the server sends when the game is over.
    GameStartResponse
    Represents a response that the server sends when the game is starting.
    MoveEndResponse
    Represents a response that the server sends when a move is ended.
    MoveStartResponse
    Represents a response that the server sends when a move is about to start.
